<S ID="388750">
(b)
</S>
<S ID="388845">
seniority adjustment of 7.5 per cent in accordance with the collective agreement (section 69);
</S>
<S ID="388850">
(c)
</S>
<S ID="388932">
appointment of staff at foreman level without holding a competition (section 88);
